  "source": "final edge-tts audio and VTT; utterances placed from measured audible bounds",
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "c01-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "你知道怎么给 AI 智能体高信号上下文吗？",
      "gapBefore": 0,
      "audioDuration": 3.288,
      "audioStart": 0,
      "spokenStart": 0.162,
      "spokenEnd": 2.648,
      "actualGapBefore": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "接下来我来告诉你，Anthropic 是怎么解决这个问题的。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.744,
      "audioStart": 2.66,
      "spokenStart": 2.808,
      "spokenEnd": 5.783,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c01-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "视频全程干货高价值，让你成为更擅长使用 AI 的人，内容较长，点点关注收藏不迷路。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 6.336,
      "audioStart": 5.73,
      "spokenStart": 5.883,
      "spokenEnd": 11.45,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "Anthropic 把上下文看成有限的注意力预算。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.144,
      "audioStart": 11.446,
      "spokenStart": 11.61,
      "spokenEnd": 13.948,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c01-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "窗口越满，真正重要的信号越容易被稀释。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.48,
      "audioStart": 13.893,
      "spokenStart": 14.048,
      "spokenEnd": 16.75,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "提示词越长，AI 智能体越可能追着旧细节跑。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.648,
      "audioStart": 16.753,
      "spokenStart": 16.91,
      "spokenEnd": 19.782,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c01-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "解决办法，是六部分高信号包：目标、规则、工具、示例、检索和状态。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.808,
      "audioStart": 19.733,
      "spokenStart": 19.882,
      "spokenEnd": 24.953,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "只保留当前约束和有效证据，目标就会重新变大。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.888,
      "audioStart": 24.955,
      "spokenStart": 25.113,
      "spokenEnd": 28.211,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c01-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "其他材料留在窗口外，需要时再检索。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.12,
      "audioStart": 28.163,
      "spokenStart": 28.311,
      "spokenEnd": 30.659,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "核心判断只有一句：给 AI 智能体支持下一步行动的最小充分上下文，并随着任务持续更新。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 6.672,
      "audioStart": 30.665,
      "spokenStart": 30.819,
      "spokenEnd": 36.721,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "先看注意力预算。",
      "gapBefore": 0.18,
      "audioDuration": 1.776,
      "audioStart": 36.746,
      "spokenStart": 36.901,
      "spokenEnd": 37.902,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.18
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "这一章会帮你判断，什么信息值得进入 AI 智能体的当前窗口。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.56,
      "audioStart": 37.839,
      "spokenStart": 38.002,
      "spokenEnd": 41.771,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "上下文不只是提示词。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.16,
      "audioStart": 41.777,
      "spokenStart": 41.931,
      "spokenEnd": 43.327,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "系统指令、工具、示例、历史记录和当前请求，都会争夺同一份注意力。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.52,
      "audioStart": 43.275,
      "spokenStart": 43.427,
      "spokenEnd": 48.171,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "材料越多，AI 智能体越难找回真正相关的信息。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.792,
      "audioStart": 48.183,
      "spokenStart": 48.331,
      "spokenEnd": 51.364,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "规则即使写进去了，也可能被旧计划和原始日志淹没。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.056,
      "audioStart": 51.313,
      "spokenStart": 51.464,
      "spokenEnd": 54.744,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "每一步开始前，只问一个问题：什么信息会改变下一步判断？",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.44,
      "audioStart": 54.746,
      "spokenStart": 54.904,
      "spokenEnd": 58.567,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "保留目标、约束、证据和当前状态，其余内容只留索引。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.704,
      "audioStart": 58.507,
      "spokenStart": 58.667,
      "spokenEnd": 62.579,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "例如准备代码修改时，仓库规则和当前错误必须在窗口里；",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.464,
      "audioStart": 62.581,
      "spokenStart": 62.739,
      "spokenEnd": 66.423,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "完整日志可以只留路径。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 2.304,
      "audioStart": 66.365,
      "spokenStart": 66.523,
      "spokenEnd": 68.043,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "最小充分不等于越短越好。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.496,
      "audioStart": 68.059,
      "spokenStart": 68.203,
      "spokenEnd": 69.939,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p06-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "验收条件、风险边界和必要证据，仍然必须完整。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.248,
      "audioStart": 69.876,
      "spokenStart": 70.039,
      "spokenEnd": 73.496,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "工具带来新证据后，要更新当前状态。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.096,
      "audioStart": 73.496,
      "spokenStart": 73.656,
      "spokenEnd": 75.972,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p07-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "用紧凑摘要替代已经完成使命的原始轨迹。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.624,
      "audioStart": 75.911,
      "spokenStart": 76.072,
      "spokenEnd": 78.925,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第一，把上下文当作有限注意力预算。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.976,
      "audioStart": 78.929,
      "spokenStart": 79.085,
      "spokenEnd": 81.289,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二，更多 token 不等于更强的信号。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.88,
      "audioStart": 81.295,
      "spokenStart": 81.449,
      "spokenEnd": 83.552,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p10-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三，随着任务变化，持续刷新上下文。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.36,
      "audioStart": 83.555,
      "spokenStart": 83.712,
      "spokenEnd": 86.287,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "接下来提高输入质量。",
      "gapBefore": 0.18,
      "audioDuration": 1.992,
      "audioStart": 86.319,
      "spokenStart": 86.467,
      "spokenEnd": 87.696,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.18
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "这一章只讲三件最有用的事：指令、工具和示例。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.888,
      "audioStart": 87.639,
      "spokenStart": 87.796,
      "spokenEnd": 90.902,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "系统指令要明确目标、边界和判断原则。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.72,
      "audioStart": 90.913,
      "spokenStart": 91.062,
      "spokenEnd": 94.034,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "不要把所有分支写死，也不要只说“把事情做好”。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.48,
      "audioStart": 93.975,
      "spokenStart": 94.134,
      "spokenEnd": 96.827,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "工具是 AI 智能体与环境的契约。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.832,
      "audioStart": 96.821,
      "spokenStart": 96.987,
      "spokenEnd": 99.039,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "名称、参数、错误和返回结果都要清楚，功能重叠的工具尽量合并。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.352,
      "audioStart": 98.976,
      "spokenStart": 99.139,
      "spokenEnd": 103.713,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "如果两个工具的边界连人都说不清，AI 智能体就更难稳定选择。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.872,
      "audioStart": 103.718,
      "spokenStart": 103.873,
      "spokenEnd": 107.971,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "示例不需要很多。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.776,
      "audioStart": 107.975,
      "spokenStart": 108.131,
      "spokenEnd": 109.104,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "两三个典型例子，展示主要模式和一条关键边界，通常比堆满例外更有效。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.712,
      "audioStart": 109.043,
      "spokenStart": 109.204,
      "spokenEnd": 114.134,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "判断一段信息是否值得保留，只看它能否改变结果、约束行为、选择工具或提供证据。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 6.576,
      "audioStart": 114.142,
      "spokenStart": 114.294,
      "spokenEnd": 120.085,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "高信号没有固定字数。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.16,
      "audioStart": 120.088,
      "spokenStart": 120.245,
      "spokenEnd": 121.638,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p07-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "只要信息承担了明确工作，它就值得保留。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.24,
      "audioStart": 121.578,
      "spokenStart": 121.738,
      "spokenEnd": 124.21,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第一，指令要清楚，但不要僵化。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.808,
      "audioStart": 124.214,
      "spokenStart": 124.37,
      "spokenEnd": 126.407,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二，保留职责单一的最小工具集。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.856,
      "audioStart": 126.405,
      "spokenStart": 126.567,
      "spokenEnd": 128.651,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p10-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三，用少量典型示例展示真正的模式。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.48,
      "audioStart": 128.654,
      "spokenStart": 128.811,
      "spokenEnd": 131.521,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "现在解决细节太多的问题。",
      "gapBefore": 0.18,
      "audioDuration": 2.352,
      "audioStart": 131.551,
      "spokenStart": 131.701,
      "spokenEnd": 133.279,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.18
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "这一章会把“全部预加载”改成“需要时再打开”。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.312,
      "audioStart": 133.223,
      "spokenStart": 133.379,
      "spokenEnd": 135.909,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "不要在任务开始前塞入所有文档。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.736,
      "audioStart": 135.916,
      "spokenStart": 136.069,
      "spokenEnd": 138.022,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "AI 智能体还没判断重点，注意力预算就已经被花掉了。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.104,
      "audioStart": 137.956,
      "spokenStart": 138.122,
      "spokenEnd": 141.448,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "上下文里先保留一张地图：文件路径、查询、链接和对象标识。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 5.496,
      "audioStart": 141.456,
      "spokenStart": 141.608,
      "spokenEnd": 146.334,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "真正需要证据时，再打开对应内容。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 2.856,
      "audioStart": 146.274,
      "spokenStart": 146.434,
      "spokenEnd": 148.516,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "例如处理大仓库时，先搜索文件名，再读取目标片段，不要一次打开整个目录。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 5.664,
      "audioStart": 148.519,
      "spokenStart": 148.676,
      "spokenEnd": 153.562,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "这就是渐进式披露。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.872,
      "audioStart": 153.559,
      "spokenStart": 153.722,
      "spokenEnd": 154.8,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "一次搜索缩小下一次搜索，AI 智能体只让正在使用的材料进入工作窗口。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.328,
      "audioStart": 154.732,
      "spokenStart": 154.9,
      "spokenEnd": 159.444,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "最实用的是混合策略：稳定规则和当前目标预先加载，变化快、细节多的材料按需检索。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 7.032,
      "audioStart": 159.457,
      "spokenStart": 159.604,
      "spokenEnd": 165.849,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "按需检索会增加探索时间，所以路径命名、搜索工具和停止条件必须清楚。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 6.144,
      "audioStart": 165.85,
      "spokenStart": 166.009,
      "spokenEnd": 171.387,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第一，保留轻量引用，不预载全部正文。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.336,
      "audioStart": 171.394,
      "spokenStart": 171.547,
      "spokenEnd": 174.117,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二，细节真正相关时再打开。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.784,
      "audioStart": 174.123,
      "spokenStart": 174.277,
      "spokenEnd": 176.289,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p10-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三，在聚焦程度和检索成本之间做取舍。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.624,
      "audioStart": 176.295,
      "spokenStart": 176.449,
      "spokenEnd": 179.309,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "长期任务还需要可恢复记忆。",
      "gapBefore": 0.18,
      "audioDuration": 2.616,
      "audioStart": 179.333,
      "spokenStart": 179.489,
      "spokenEnd": 181.339,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.18
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "这一章会比较压缩、笔记和专门 Agent。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.192,
      "audioStart": 181.276,
      "spokenStart": 181.439,
      "spokenEnd": 183.837,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "窗口快满时，把轨迹压缩成连续性摘要。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.216,
      "audioStart": 183.844,
      "spokenStart": 183.997,
      "spokenEnd": 186.452,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "只带上决定、约束、证据、未决问题和下一步动作。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.2,
      "audioStart": 186.398,
      "spokenStart": 186.552,
      "spokenEnd": 189.988,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "压缩要先保证不漏关键信息。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.568,
      "audioStart": 189.988,
      "spokenStart": 190.148,
      "spokenEnd": 191.951,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "宁可多带一点，也不要丢掉后来无法恢复的约束。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.576,
      "audioStart": 191.896,
      "spokenStart": 192.051,
      "spokenEnd": 194.846,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "结构化笔记适合保存进度和工作状态。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.24,
      "audioStart": 194.858,
      "spokenStart": 195.006,
      "spokenEnd": 197.475,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "到达里程碑就更新笔记，用它替代冗长的原始历史。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.936,
      "audioStart": 197.421,
      "spokenStart": 197.575,
      "spokenEnd": 200.737,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "一份合格的交接摘要，必须保留目标、决定、证据、未知项和下一步动作。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 5.664,
      "audioStart": 200.742,
      "spokenStart": 200.897,
      "spokenEnd": 205.785,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "只有独立深挖的价值超过协调成本时，才使用专门 Agent。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.248,
      "audioStart": 205.779,
      "spokenStart": 205.945,
      "spokenEnd": 209.413,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p06-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "主 Agent 只接收压缩后的结论。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 2.616,
      "audioStart": 209.352,
      "spokenStart": 209.513,
      "spokenEnd": 211.331,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "持续对话适合压缩，有里程碑的工作适合笔记，独立研究才考虑专门 Agent。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 5.208,
      "audioStart": 211.33,
      "spokenStart": 211.491,
      "spokenEnd": 215.925,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第一，用高召回摘要压缩长轨迹。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3,
      "audioStart": 215.929,
      "spokenStart": 216.085,
      "spokenEnd": 218.308,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二，把持久状态写进结构化笔记。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.024,
      "audioStart": 218.314,
      "spokenStart": 218.468,
      "spokenEnd": 220.731,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p10-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三，专门 Agent 只用于值得并行深挖的问题。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.552,
      "audioStart": 220.735,
      "spokenStart": 220.891,
      "spokenEnd": 223.661,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "最后把方法装进一个可复用工具。",
      "gapBefore": 0.18,
      "audioDuration": 2.736,
      "audioStart": 223.693,
      "spokenStart": 223.841,
      "spokenEnd": 225.815,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.18
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c06-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "这一章会完成六部分高信号上下文包。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.024,
      "audioStart": 225.759,
      "spokenStart": 225.915,
      "spokenEnd": 228.164,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第一组是结果目标和运行规则。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.64,
      "audioStart": 228.167,
      "spokenStart": 228.324,
      "spokenEnd": 230.193,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c06-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "写清交付物、验收条件、权限、风险边界和停止条件。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.728,
      "audioStart": 230.141,
      "spokenStart": 230.293,
      "spokenEnd": 234.256,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二组是工具地图和典型示例。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.856,
      "audioStart": 234.262,
      "spokenStart": 234.416,
      "spokenEnd": 236.497,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c06-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "说明工具何时使用，并用少量例子展示主要模式。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.96,
      "audioStart": 236.442,
      "spokenStart": 236.597,
      "spokenEnd": 239.774,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三组是检索索引和工作状态。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.736,
      "audioStart": 239.777,
      "spokenStart": 239.934,
      "spokenEnd": 241.892,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c06-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "记录证据入口、当前重点、关键决定、未知项和下一步动作。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.728,
      "audioStart": 241.844,
      "spokenStart": 241.992,
      "spokenEnd": 245.966,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "真正执行时，每个字段都要能回答一个问题：AI 智能体下一步该做什么？",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 5.208,
      "audioStart": 245.963,
      "spokenStart": 246.126,
      "spokenEnd": 250.558,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "每到一个里程碑，就更新状态并归档旧轨迹。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.576,
      "audioStart": 250.561,
      "spokenStart": 250.718,
      "spokenEnd": 253.538,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p06-u02",
      "sceneId": "c06-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "这样长期任务不会依赖一段不断膨胀的对话。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.552,
      "audioStart": 253.481,
      "spokenStart": 253.638,
      "spokenEnd": 256.405,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "上下文包要足够短，方便快速检查；",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.096,
      "audioStart": 256.413,
      "spokenStart": 256.565,
      "spokenEnd": 258.89,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p07-u02",
      "sceneId": "c06-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "也要足够完整，不让 AI 智能体猜关键约束。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.6,
      "audioStart": 258.832,
      "spokenStart": 258.99,
      "spokenEnd": 261.811,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第一，用目标和规则锚定 AI 智能体。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.072,
      "audioStart": 261.814,
      "spokenStart": 261.971,
      "spokenEnd": 264.267,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二，用工具、示例和检索索引指导行动。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.672,
      "audioStart": 264.271,
      "spokenStart": 264.427,
      "spokenEnd": 267.323,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p10-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三，用持续更新的工作状态保持连续性。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.576,
      "audioStart": 267.331,
      "spokenStart": 267.483,
      "spokenEnd": 270.308,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c07-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "AI 智能体忘记重点，往往不是信息太少，而是没有区分的信息太多。",
      "gapBefore": 0.18,
      "audioDuration": 4.92,
      "audioStart": 270.328,
      "spokenStart": 270.488,
      "spokenEnd": 274.63,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.18
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c07-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第一，管理完整上下文，只保留会改变下一步判断的信息。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.32,
      "audioStart": 274.633,
      "spokenStart": 274.79,
      "spokenEnd": 278.335,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c07-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二，提高信号质量，用清楚指令、最小工具集和典型示例指导行动。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 5.496,
      "audioStart": 278.343,
      "spokenStart": 278.495,
      "spokenEnd": 283.231,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c07-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三，细节按需检索，长任务用压缩、笔记和工作状态保持连续性。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 5.472,
      "audioStart": 283.237,
      "spokenStart": 283.391,
      "spokenEnd": 288.09,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c07-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "最后带走六部分上下文包：目标、规则、工具、示例、检索和状态。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 5.568,
      "audioStart": 288.101,
      "spokenStart": 288.25,
      "spokenEnd": 293.062,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c07-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "下一次开始长期任务前，先花一分钟写好这六部分，再让 AI 智能体行动。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 5.328,
      "audioStart": 293.069,
      "spokenStart": 293.222,
      "spokenEnd": 297.776,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
